As result has to be first column sorted, then row sorted.
So, loop through `c1 to c2` & add cells from `r1 to r2 for each column.`

```
class Solution {
    public List<String> cellsInRange(String s) {
        char c1 = s.charAt(0);
        char r1 = s.charAt(1);

        char c2 = s.charAt(3);
        char r2 = s.charAt(4);

        List<String> res = new ArrayList<>();
        while (c1 <= c2) {
            char temp = r1;
            while (temp <= r2) {
                res.add(c1 + "" + temp);
                ++temp;
            }
            ++c1;
        }
        return res;
    }
}
```

